    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Sauerkraut]]></title>
    <link href="http://ScottWeinstein.github.com/Recipes/blog/2012/12/30/sauerkraut/"/>
    <updated>2012-12-30T18:37:00-05:00</updated>
    <id>http://ScottWeinstein.github.com/Recipes/blog/2012/12/30/sauerkraut</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2>Ingredient</h2>

<ul>
<li>3-4 Kg Cabbage</li>
<li><p>5 g salt/Kg cabbage</p></li>
<li><p>1 L water</p></li>
<li>15 g salt</li>
</ul>


<h2>Steps</h2>

<ul>
<li>Boil salt &amp; water, let cool</li>
<li>Shred cabbage</li>
<li>Mix salt and cabbage</li>
<li>Pack tightly into crock</li>
<li>Place stones</li>
<li>Cover w/ salt water if required</li>
<li>Cover w/ container and fill channel w/ salt water</li>
<li>Wait 3-6 weeks</li>
</ul>

